Loan Eligibility Predictor
https://img.shields.io/badge/Prediction-AI%2520Powered-blue https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.8%252B-green https://img.shields.io/badge/Web%2520UI-Streamlit-red

A Machine Learning-based web application that predicts whether a loan applicant is eligible for approval based on personal and financial details.

